name: Karina Strimersha
description:
Russian speaking twitch streamer, lets player and vlogger.

Trigger word: young woman

Examples generated on the Deliberate model.

I recommend that you first generate the desired image, and then change the face using hypernetwork in the inpaint tab:

Inpaint settings:

  1. Resize mode - Just resize

  2. Mask mode - Inpaint masked

  3. Masked content - original

  4. Inpaint area - Only masked

  5. Width and Height - 512x512 or higher

  6. Don't forget to switch to a random seed

  7. Experiment with Denoising strength (0.3 - 0.9) and Only masked padding, pixels (10-60)
